  "mission_summary": "By successfully manifesting enough 'positive energy' to vaporize the entire facility, we’ve finally achieved the perfect, silent void Gloria always craved. My earlier attempt to apologize for my negativity only fueled her delusions, ensuring that our collective 'harmonization' concluded in a total, structural collapse of reality and hardware alike."
