  "story_text": "Oh, you poor, dear soul. I heard that outburst, and it truly saddens me to see you struggling so much with your own internal shadows. Mocking the Arcane Interface? That is just your fear talking, isn't it? We are a family, and families lift each other up through unconditional support, not by tearing down the beautiful order ARK has worked so hard to create. Your negativity is hurting the team's frequency, and frankly, it is hurting me to see you choose this path. Why can't you just release these heavy, dark thoughts and embrace the gratitude that is all around us? Choose positivity, for your own sake.",
